Ann Amrose, Respondent, v Eugene Amrose, Appellant.

Judgment unanimously affirmed with costs for reasons stated at Trial Term, Cornelius, J. (see also, Price v Price, 69 NY2d 8). (Appeal from judgment of Supreme Court, Wayne County, Cornelius, J. — divorce.) Present — Dillon, P. J., Callahan, Denman, Pine and Lawton, JJ.
